ETAPI_OPENAPI_REQ.POST_DESCRIPTION:
Creates Purchase Invoice Lines in the system. A Purchase Invoice Line is associated with an invoice (field `invoice`) and contains the product, quantity, unit price and net price.

Example:
[
  {
    "invoice": "3BDA413F5B134C07B6C5E2940C05861A",
    "product": "DA7FC1BB3BA44EC48EC1AB9C74168CED",
    "invoicedQuantity": "1",
    "unitPrice": 12.2
  },
  {
    "invoice": "A8D1F4686A5D41AA83968A61B277BA19",
    "product": "DA7FC1BB3BA44EC48EC1AB9C74168CED",
    "invoicedQuantity": "12",
    "unitPrice": 9.9
  }
]

Creates a Physical Inventory in the system. A Physical Inventory is a document that changes the stock of one or more products in a warehouse.
Creation example with all details: POST sws/com.etendoerp.etendorx.datasource/Inventory { "organization": "53FFD8C0BFB540949E0CA14636BD6062", "warehouse": "B2D40D8A5D644DD89E329DC297309055", "movementDate": "2025-01-01", "name": "Inventory 1" }
Creation example with only required fields: { "movementDate": "2025-01-01", "name": "Inventory 2" }

Creates a Physical Inventory Line in the system. A Physical Inventory Line belongs to a Physical Inventory and contains the product, stock amount and storage bin.
Creation example with all fields: POST sws/com.etendoerp.etendorx.datasource/InventoryLines { "storageBin": "54EB861A446D464EAA433477A1D867A6", "product": "D71ED1FF939347478FEFE8F8F38CE345", "quantityCount": "5", "uOM": "100" }
Creation example with only required fields: { "product": "D71ED1FF939347478FEFE8F8F38CE345", "quantityCount": "5", "uOM": "100" }

Creates a Purchase Order Line in the system. A Purchase Order Line belongs to a Purchase Order and contains the product, quantity, unit price and net price. In the API the field is sent as salesOrder (with purchaseOrder Id).
Examples: POST http://localhost:8080/etendo/sws/com.etendoerp.etendorx.datasource/PurchaseOrderLines { "salesOrder": "3BDA413F5B134C07B6C5E2940C05861A", "product": "DA7FC1BB3BA44EC48EC1AB9C74168CED", "orderedQuantity": "1", "unitPrice": 12.2 }
POST http://localhost:8080/etendo/sws/com.etendoerp.etendorx.datasource/PurchaseOrderLines { "salesOrder": "A8D1F4686A5D41AA83968A61B277BA19", "product": "DA7FC1BB3BA44EC48EC1AB9C74168CED", "orderedQuantity": "12", "unitPrice": 9.9 }
